od resources on a small island, even when food is patchily distributed in urbanized habitats.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Nakamoto, Atsushi", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Kinjo, Kazumitsu", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/d0b06e8b1b1eddb241ec224a16a30ac3", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/04441cb97b74ebad5dd42c47a10e870785981fb5b8394f48de27585644c99a23", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/F9UCAZ9F", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/F9UCAZ9F", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/669b3563cbd2390217e841f92e8e0de9!/b278347-280826", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "2", "pages": "387", "title": "Acta Chiropterologica", "volume": "14"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/d0b06e8b1b1eddb241ec224a16a30ac3"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:F9UCAZ9F"}, {"identifier": "10.3161/150811012X661701"}], "communities": [{"id": "biosyslit"}, {"id": "batlit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid", "pid_value": "13445092"}}]}}, "title": "Ranging Patterns and Habitat Use of a Solitary Flying Fox (Pteropus dasymallus) on Okinawa-jima Isla